item.title: Sample Packs from Printing Companies
item.description: I’ve been busy the last couple of months putting things in place to get Ilumia Images up and running as its own business and as part of that I needed some printing done for business cards and some other items. I spent quite a bit of time on Google looking at options etc. and send off for sample print packs from 4 different printers - Printed.com - Solopress.com - digitalprinting.
